extends ../../layout-en

block content

  .container-full
    .container

      h1.h3.centered.vertical-space-m DevMeetings: workshops for passionate software developers.
      p.h5.centered Offered in Pay What You Want model.
      .workshop-holder.row.vertical-space-m
        .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
          .videos 
            <iframe width="854" height="510" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/De17BOe1GnE?rel=0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
    .container            
      .row.vertical-space-m
        h2.h3.centered Upcoming workshops
      .workshop-holder.row.vertical-space-m
        .col-sm-6.col-xs-12
          .box
            .box-image
              a(href='/en/info/ecmaScript6')
                img.img-responsive.workshop-img(src='/img/static/workshops/es6_devmeeting_krk.jpg' alt='')
            .box-details
              a(href='/en/info/ecmaScript6')
                h3.h4 Teaser ES6
              p
                | The workshops are dedicated to the creation of application with the help of ECMA Script 6. It is directed at people knowledgeable about JavaScript as well as programmers of other languages (java, php, ruby), who want to immediately enter the current language specification. 
              p
                span.fa.fa-map-marker.fa-lg.fa-fw
                | &nbsp;<strong>Kraków</strong>
              p
                span.fa.fa-calendar.fa-lg.fa-fw
                | &nbsp; <strong>20th of June 2015</strong>
              p.btn-holder
                a.btn.btn-dev(href='/en/info/ecmaScript6') Register

        .col-sm-6.col-xs-12
          .box
            .box-image
              a(href='/en/info/react')
                img.img-responsive.workshop-img(src='/img/static/workshops/teaser_devm_react.png' alt='')
            .box-details
              a(href='/en/info/react')
                h3.h4 Teaser React
              p
                | All-day workshops of the React library, together with Redux, as an implementation of the state container. Discover the Facebook library, which allows for the creation of efficient applications of the Singe Page Apps type, which gains more and more popularity. 
              p
                span.fa.fa-map-marker.fa-lg.fa-fw
                | &nbsp;<strong>Kraków</strong>
              p
                span.fa.fa-calendar.fa-lg.fa-fw
                | &nbsp; <strong>20th of June 2015</strong>
              p.btn-holder
                a.btn.btn-dev(href='/en/info/react') Register
     
      .workshop-holder.row
        .col-sm-6.col-xs-12
          .box
            .box-image
              a(href='/en/info/ionic')
                img.img-responsive.workshop-img(src='/img/static/workshops/teaser_devm_ionic.png' alt='')
            .box-details
              a(href='/en/info/ionic')
                h3.h4 Teaser Ionic
              p
                | Workshops with Ionic Framework, which allows for the creation of mobile hybrid applications based on JS. During the workshops, you will get to know the SDK, creation aspects of the user interface, as well as an opportunity to access the mobile device’s resources.  
              p
                span.fa.fa-map-marker.fa-lg.fa-fw
                | &nbsp;<strong>Kraków</strong>
              p
                span.fa.fa-calendar.fa-lg.fa-fw
                | &nbsp; <strong>20th of June 2015</strong>
              p.btn-holder
                a.btn.btn-dev(href='/en/info/ionic') Register

        .col-sm-6.col-xs-12
          .box
            .box-image
              a(href='/en/info/angular-2')
                img.img-responsive.workshop-img(src='/img/static/workshops/teaser_devm_angular_2.png' alt='')
            .box-details
              a(href='/en/info/angular-2')
                h3.h4 Teaser Angular 2
              p
                | Angular 2 is still in its beta state, but more and more developer teams use it for production purposes. We are inviting you for all-day workshops with Angular 2, together with TypeScript and ES2015.
              p
                span.fa.fa-map-marker.fa-lg.fa-fw
                | &nbsp;<strong>Kraków</strong>
              p
                span.fa.fa-calendar.fa-lg.fa-fw
                | &nbsp; <strong>20th of June 2015</strong>
              p.btn-holder
                a.btn.btn-dev(href='/en/info/angular-2') Register

